devdoc.author: Ivan Carneiro
devdoc.details: Implements features like bid increments, automatic extensions, and refunds with commission

params._bidIncrement: The minimum bid increment (in percentage), if not specified, will be 2%.
params._duration: The duration of the auction (in seconds), e.g. (5min = 300sec; 10min = 600sec; 1h = 3600sec; 1d = 86400sec).
params._initValue: The initial value of the auction item.

devdoc.title: AuctETH - A smart contract for Ethereum-based auctions
